This month, South African consumers can enjoy the best value-for-money data deals on large mobile data bundles the country has ever seen. Telkom’s Big Deal for April 2019 offers subscribers 20GB data, 1,500 all-network minutes, 3,000 Telkom minutes, 50GB video, 10GB music streaming, and 2GB IM data for R499 per month. Not to be outdone, Vodacom launched its best ever data deal on 5 April – 60GB anytime data and 30GB after-hours data (12am – 5am) for R299 per month. MTN has also joined the big data party with its Double Your Data promotion, offering 20GB anytime data, 14 GB streaming data and 20GB Night Express data (12am – 6am) for R199 per month. The company is also offering a 50GB anytime data contract for R399 per month, which is aimed at the business market. The images below provide an overview of the big data deals available this month. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-303724" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Vodacom-deal.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Vodacom-deal.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Vodacom-deal-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-303840" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/MTN-mega-deal.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/MTN-mega-deal.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/MTN-mega-deal-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-303900" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/MTN-50GB.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/